		<td><b>Where to go now?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm making my own NES emulator, and all the CPU emulation is working. But now I need to start the PPU emulation. But the question is, how can I start it?
<br />
<br />I've downloaded all the DOCs existing in this site, but i don't know where ti start reading. Can anyone help me to walk this path?
<br />
<br />Please I need to know what I must learn from know. All I found in the boards are questions about specific topics in the PPU emulation.
<br />
<br />Thank you guys...

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


